2026-06-04 13:55:14,354 | DEBUG    |       if r > unicode.MaxASCII {
2026-06-04 13:55:14,354 | DEBUG    |           escapeBuf = fmt.Appendf(escapeBuf[:0], "\\u%04x", r) // 5+ digits for non-BMP → invalid escape
