2026-06-04 13:55:14,356 | DEBUG    |   
2026-06-04 13:55:14,356 | DEBUG    |   - **Assumption:** Consumers expect RFC-compliant `\u` escaping, not the previous malformed five-digit form; fixing is a behavior correction, not an API break.
